data.description: BOATERS DREAM .. When you enter this Open Floorplan Designed Home with a Hurricane Impact- Etched Palm Tree- Glass Front Door -  your eyes are drawn immediately to the Outside Water. From your Custom Designed Deep Pool with New Extended Sun Deck - New PEBBLE TECH surfacing throughout - and all New Pavers (2021) surrounding the Pool. New Pool Heating / Cooling System (2021) Then, the Boater's DREAM, not 1 but 2 Boat Lifts. One up to 10,000 Pound Capacity  & one up to 20,000 Pound Capacity ( less than 4 yrs 'new' ). Deep Water For Sailboats & You'll be out to Sea in just 5 minutes through World Renowned  John's Pass. The Oversized Deck is perfect for all your relaxation time over the Water - Enjoying Sunsets and Entertaining many friends that will be visiting this Home because it's less than 10 minutes' walk to the BEACH. Plus, the MADEIRA BOAT PARADE passes right by your deck twice! The lush Tropical yard (front & back) has been redesigned(2021) and maintained by current owners to make yard work a breeze. Step back inside to the Amazing Sunroom with 5 sliding doors to west and north (3 with sliding Plantation Blinds) that allow the beautiful Sunlight in year round. Open the north sliding doors year round to the New Porch Roof and Screening (2022) area for those wonderful Florida Breezes -  Or keep them closed and watch how efficient your new Oct 2022 TRANE AC really is (downstairs unit). There are 3 Bedrooms and 2 Bathrooms Downstairs on the Main Floor (1 with a brand new 2023 Laundry room) , including a downstairs En-suite MASTER Bedroom complete with a Walk-in Closet & Private Sliding Doors to the Pool & Lounging Area.  The Second  En-Suite Master is Upstairs with a Balcony overlooking the Intracoastal Waterway - Plus a Fully Remodeled Bathroom (2022).  The Upstairs Addition is a must-see with it's New Beautiful Wooden Stairs with 2 closets (1 up & 1 down) for extra STORAGE / Closet Space.  Upstairs, You will also find another huge En-Suite Guest Bedroom to the left, a Split Floorplan perfect for Privacy. The Chefs Kitchen has plenty of storage for all your Cooking Gadgets and 2 Breakfast Bars with seating up to 8. The Appliances are Jenn air refrigerator, Dishwasher, & Stove/oven with Down Draft Fan. The new 2023 built-in High Ponte is an all in 1 microwave with Convection Grill Roast features included. All protected by the house water softener and Home Appliances Choice Warranty.  The Dining room area, located by the kitchen, with sliding doors to the screen room can easily accommodate your large family table. The Family room, open near the kitchen, allows you to cook and enjoy your time with Family & Friends too. Which you will have plenty of parking for with the circular driveway and double garage with extended driveway. Whole House is protected under a pest control plan that includes quarterly Inspections . Welcome to Florida Waterfront Living . 5 Bedroom / 4 Bath With over 2800 Sq Ft of Living Space.. Great Family Home at a Good Price.. No Water During Last Storm.
